data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET! One buyers loss is another ones gain, let it be yours! Situated in the heart of Dix River Estates, check out this stunning 4 bedroom, 4.5 bath, 5,300 sqft luxury home! Beautiful hardwood flooring welcomes you into a large, bright living room. Custom cabinetry, granite counter-tops, stainless steel appliances (gas stove), and a cozy fireplace can be found in the open concept kitchen/den! Huge master suite w/ double tray ceilings, walk in closet and dressing room, over-sized walk in shower, and double granite vanities. Both guest rooms on the first floor offer walk in closets, and en bathrooms with granite counter-tops. The second floor boasts a massive loft w/ separate heating and air wall unit. The 1,900 sqft basement includes a bonus room (5th bedroom potential) w/ a full bath, and a massive space currently used for a home theater. A covered back patio w/ fireplace and irrigated lawn are great for entertaining. The over-sized upper and lower garages are perfect for storage, and the geothermal system and spray foam insulation keep utilities low. Move quickly, this will beautiful home will not last!
